{"tid":2462010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"復必泰疫苗│保安經理行山猝死　身體健康非長期病患　一周前打針","createTime":"2021-03-25T17:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T17:29:11.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"64dd6a13d36abc15a0c4b33c25adcc84647c2df2","tid":2462010,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"一名59歲男子今早於西貢麥理浩徑第二段行山期間昏迷，他由飛行服務隊送往東區醫院後證實不治。衞生署晚上表示，59歲男子於7日前（3月18日）在彩虹道羽毛球中心社區疫苗接種中心接種復必泰新冠疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，59歲死者李國威任職保安經理，與家人同住九龍灣。李是資深行山者，一向身體健康，無長期病患及做手術等紀錄，最近亦未有出現不適，行動自如，今早如常獨自出發前往麥理浩徑行山，至早上9時仍有向妻子傳短訊報告位置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210325/451876447024320512854391.jpeg/0UPC77x9rmCEN4aGg0VHr02wz9ICV25yrHQE46x0BOM?v=w1760\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210325%2F451876447024320512854391.jpeg%2F0UPC77x9rmCEN4aGg0VHr02wz9ICV25yrHQE46x0BOM%3Fv%3Dw1760&h=a55e00af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男子由飛行服務隊送往東區醫院後證實不治。（「來源：無綫電視」）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210325/451728712900022272462975.jpeg/BZNls74K5evr3ZhWSjbLsYtC-QdD2sfD5VHG0OVRxtA?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210325%2F451728712900022272462975.jpeg%2FBZNls74K5evr3ZhWSjbLsYtC-QdD2sfD5VHG0OVRxtA%3Fv%3Dw960&h=7bec341f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20201220/417295289985011712520918.jpeg/R6fun3TKXq1R2xmVk8SV2Ysynri4geAkJ7m0Bie5tAY?v=w960\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20201220%2F417295289985011712520918.jpeg%2FR6fun3TKXq1R2xmVk8SV2Ysynri4geAkJ7m0Bie5tAY%3Fv%3Dw960&h=1a207e31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n衞生署晚上公布，醫管局接獲一名59歲男子，今日於西貢被遠足人士發現失去知覺，由政府飛行服務隊送往東區醫院後證實死亡。衞生署指男子於3月18日在彩虹道羽毛球中心社區疫苗接種中心接種復必泰新冠疫苗，署方指死者在接種後逗留在接種中心觀察期間並沒有不適紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，李國威有5年獨自行山經驗，據悉他過去並無長期病及做手術等紀錄，他7日前（3月18日）接種復必泰新冠疫苗，最近亦未有出現不適及行動自如。於今早7時許，李如常獨自出發前往行山，至早上9時仍有向妻子傳短訊及自拍，透露自己由西灣村經麥理浩徑前往東壩方向。<br />\n<br />\n至早上11時，有行山人士途經麥理浩徑二段，發現李倒臥地上，逐漸失去知覺及呼吸困難，於是報警求助，及為李進行心肺復蘇術，事主其後由飛行服務隊送往東區醫院搶救，惟於中午12時39分證實不治。警方將案列作送院時死亡，死因有待進一步調查。"},{"pid":"b9e9aeed965da87d3621406c666dc01fdcefd489","tid":2462010,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:07:05.000Z","msg":"又派彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e19e851b81dd97aaaf49679d31a26b8d43fbd9","tid":2462010,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T17:08:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYbuKntE6gwFPtHpeiVwqhAMpanP6SQyDPZ1igLAYvPdw?filename=PMicjYU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPMicjYU.gif&h=98f9374e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmURea3aX2WaHt9syzqjiuDJpPmRv8RoqZ4ramqPDBiyAZ?filename=0YngMDV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YngMDV.gif&h=da5a544a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTBxLzabUiahjBo2S8vVbmCMsiDRXGDJnbJqXQ9jj4Tkd?filename=fKLVhLA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfKLVhLA.gif&h=a8f444f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSwE1gS7stPvL7BDBWZtBFKRfwgwHHg4u1tTrV6VRyy1i?filename=ViBtCLB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FViBtCLB.jpg&h=b721657b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVZEDy7MQ8fANQYPLWuAVUneFov6UhUepDThdHjVbvTBe?filename=LkmpVxg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLkmpVxg.gif&h=d39a37c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZC3f4dtESiFW6oQch4EUEhoRibuLWAvwcyp53CqS2n7B?filename=BxzKVxh.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBxzKVxh.gif&h=bb2772d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWH2eqkni